;; flags: rd ad; QUERY: 1, ANSWER: 0, AUTHORITY: 0, ADDITIONAL: 1

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:
; EDNS: version 0; flags: ; udp: 4096

;; QUESTION SECTION:
;aplus.beta.gouv.fr.	IN	 TXT
response:
;; opcode: QUERY, status: NOERROR, id: 60035
;; flags: qr rd ra; QUERY: 1, ANSWER: 1, AUTHORITY: 0, ADDITIONAL: 1

;; OPT PSEUDOSECTION:
; EDNS: version 0; flags: ; udp: 1232

;; QUESTION SECTION:
;aplus.beta.gouv.fr.	IN	 TXT

;; ANSWER SECTION:
aplus.beta.gouv.fr.	300	IN	TXT	"v=spf1 include:spf.mailjet.com include:sendgrid.net include:_spf.alwaysdata.com ~all"
